name: Employee Checkin Report
query:
SELECT
    name as "ID:Link/Employee Checkin:180",
    employee as "Employee ID:Link/Employee:100",
    employee_name as "Full Name::100",
    log_type as "Log Type::100",
    cast(time as date) as "Date::120",
    cast(time as time) as "Time::120"
FROM
    `tabEmployee Checkin`
